🧠 Why Transformers Matter

Transformers enable:

Parallel sequence processing

Long-range dependency learning

Transfer learning at scale

Modern NLP systems like ChatGPT

Large language models such as GPT-3

They form the backbone of today’s Generative AI revolution.

